Name: STRAY CAT
About the game: STRAY CAT This is a small game about a homeless cat who decided to save money for a new home. 2D platformer with a side view, where you will play as a brave cat who decided to collect all the coins on his way and destroy evil opponents. In the game you will definitely have to: - Collect coins; - Dodge sharp sawing discs and projectiles; - Search for the key to the cave; - Fight with enemies; - Jump on trampolines; - Climbing vines; - Push crates; Key Features: - Suitable for children (The game is not very difficult and there is no blood in it); - The game has original author's graphics; - Pleasant soundtrack.
